      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 14.9,
      "text": "When you start your pattern, there is a rhythm to your pattern. It's not just really fast all the way through, it's not slow all the way through. There's a slow, fast, and you get a 1.3 or a 1.4."
    },
    {
      "start": 14.9,
      "end": 30.980000000000004,
      "text": "So, each individual category, you need to obviously get as high as you can. If you're a black belt, generally, depending on the competition, you will be scored from a 1.3. So, 1.3 would be your average that you start from."
    },
    {
      "start": 30.980000000000004,
      "end": 44.56,
      "text": "So, say your pattern speed was above average, you might get scored a 1.4 for now. Say your rhythm was only about average."
    },
    {
      "start": 44.9,
      "end": 57.72,
      "text": "It wasn't amazing. It might be just a 1.3, but let's say you didn't shout very loud. So, your expression of energy, your average was 1.3. It might drop to say, let's say, a 1.0."
    },
    {
      "start": 59.839999999999996,
      "end": 61.5,
      "text": "I think I got enough."
    },
    {
